channel.title: Where is it?
channel.description:
hey peeps...
my favorite source of all time has been chassyscape..
i originally used it as a base when i started coding... i changed everything in it.. gave chassy credit in the intro and all that.. and the thing broke one day.. i quit coding, and i come back 3 months later to try at chassyscape again and to perfect the 85% plan my server had..
but now i cant find the chassyscape source? or it's download? so.. im asknig for some assistance? can someone help me? i wont rest till i have that source again :( it was the best source i had coded.. and i was hoping to get it back..
Chassy13 :P i'll be looking for u too XD
*note this might be in wrong section? im an old coder and an old moparscape person.. so i might have forgotten where some things should be posted -.-*
